item.title: Hola world
item.author: josfemova@gmail.com (José Morales)
item.description: Why I made this blog I need a place to you know…blog about stuff I do, so naturally, I searched for a hugo theme that I liked and welp…here we are. What to expect I do a lot of stuff with different microcontrollers, and I’m planning on doing some guides with some of them. I’m also working in some interesting science/data aquisition projects, so I will probably post about that when I get the time to do so.
